 President Muhammadu Buhari has said that the new ministers who will be sworn in next week will receive clear implementation targets tied to their portfolios. The President made the announcement on Wednesday via his official Twitter page. The incoming Ministers, who will be sworn in next week, will receive clear implementation targets tied to their portfolios. We will ensure these targets are complied with; performance will be monitored by the Office of the Secretary to the Government of the Federation. — Muhammadu Buhari (@MBuhari) August 14, 2019 https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js The post President Buhari Sets “clear implementation targets” For Incoming Ministers appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija